high_descs: Turn to your left and walk towards the refrigerator, then make a right just past the refrigerator and walk to the sink across from you.
Pick up the knife to the left of the forks on the left, covered portion of the sink.
Turn around and walk to the kitchen table just past the refrigerator, to the left.
Cut the head of lettuce, between the bottle of wine and the black cooking pot, into slices.
Turn to your right and walk toward the refrigerator, then turn slightly to your right and walk across the kitchen to the stove.
Place the knife in the fry pan on the back, right burner of the stove.
Turn around and walk across the kitchen, back to the table, past the refrigerator.
Pick up the end slice of lettuce, closest to you, on the table.
Turn around and walk back across the kitchen, to the stove, with the slice of lettuce.
Place the slice of lettuce in the pan, on the back, right burner of the stove, to the left of the knife.
Pick up the fry pan from the stove, containing the knife and the slice of lettuce.
Turn around and walk to the refrigerator.
Place the fry pan containing the knife and the slice of lettuce in the refrigerator, on the top shelf, between the pepper and the egg.
anns.task_desc: Put a fry pan containing a knife and slice of lettuce, in the refrigerator.

high_descs: Turn left, walk, turn left again and go to the sink.
Take the knife on the sink.
Turn around and walk toward the fridge. Then turn left, the right and walk to the kitchen table.
Cut the lettuce on the table.
Turn around, turn left, walk past the fridge, then turn right and go to the stove.
Put the knife in the pan on the back left burner.
Turn around and walk back to the kitchen table.
Take a slice of lettuce.
Turn around and walk back to the stove.
Put the lettuce in the pan with the knife.
Take the pan from the stove.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge door, put the pan inside, and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with a knife and lettuce slice in the fridge.
